@startuml
|Guest User|
start
:Click on Register Button;
:Fill Registration Form (Email, Password, Name);
:Submit Form;
|System|
if (Valid Inputs?) then (yes)
    :Create New Account;
    :Send Confirmation Email;
    :Redirect to Login;
else (no)
    :Show Error Message;
    :Ask to Re-enter Details;
endif
stop
@enduml
